<SYNC Start=5096986><P Class=KRCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=5124749><P Class=KRCC>
그녀를 데려가.
<SYNC Start=5125753><P Class=KRCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=5128701><P Class=KRCC>
